						               													<description>MouseHunt: The Board Game is a board game implementation of the Facebook game MouseHunt developed by hitGrab Inc.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game players take on the role of Mouse Hunters in the fantasy kingdom of Gnawnia. They arm mighty weapons to bases and set out cheese to attract different mice ranging from the mundane to the fantastic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first hunter to catch all the mice on his list wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During their turn a hunter rolls a die to determine, which mouse they attracted. A second die roll will determine, if the trap trap is strong enough to catch the mouse. Weapons, bases, bait and location will modify the attraction and catch rolls. Catching a mouse will get you a bounty, but if you miss other hunters at the location will have a shot at catching the same mouse.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use the bounty to buy improved weapons, better bait and travel the kingdom to complete your hunting assignment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
